---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Litcode Helper"
  description="Privacy policy for Litcode Helper, a browser extension for saving LeetCode solutions to GitHub."
  canonicalPath="/privacy/"
>
  <article class="wrap privacy">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
    <h1>Litcode Helper Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: May 30, 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Stored Locally</h2>
      <p>
        Litcode Helper stores settings in the user's browser, including GitHub owner, repository,
        branch, timezone, duplicate preference, upload status, retry queue, and the fine-grained
        GitHub token provided by the user.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Sent To GitHub</h2>
      <p>
        When a solution is saved, Litcode Helper sends the problem title, problem URL, problem
        statement, language, submitted code, and target file path to GitHub's API. This data is sent
        only to the repository configured by the user.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>No Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        Litcode Helper does not use analytics, advertising, tracking pixels, telemetry, or a backend
        server. Data is not sold or shared with third parties.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>GitHub Token</h2>
      <p>
        The GitHub token is stored locally in browser extension storage and is used only for GitHub
        API requests needed to create or update files in the configured repository.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: clamp(56px, 9vw, 92px) 0 28px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #b93c2a;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 62px);
    line-height: 1;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .updated {
    color: #665f54;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  section {
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(22, 19, 15, 0.22);
    margin-top: 28px;
    max-width: 760px;
    padding-top: 22px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  p {
    color: #3b362f;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
</style>
